description: Essex Police are seeking the extradition of 40-year-old Ronan Hughes from County Monaghan.
title: Essex lorry deaths: Ronan Hughes denied bail
title_page: Essex lorry deaths: Ronan Hughes denied bail - BBC News
maintext: The judge said he found Mr Hughes' claim of a lack of awareness of his financial affairs unconvincing. A further hearing will be held in Dublin on 7 May.
